characterCustomizations.biography: Asylus, was once a warrior taught by her father before he had passed into the void never to be herd from again. She was alone through most of her life on the outskirts of Silvermoon. She had weilded her mighty two handed sword and learn quite quickly how to vanquish her foes. She then, in Pandaria was approached by Shao Li. An old monk wanting to teach his thunderfist technique to one last pupil before his passing. Asylus was sent on a mission that was only for the feint of heart. If one was not in touch with there true selves, then they would be corrupted by the sha in which their heart lied in. Asylus nervous, wanted the power of the Thunderfist and went for the test. Her wits was the only thing she had to endure. Nothign physical. She drank a potion Masteer Shao Li gave her and she embarked into seeing the nether. She was shown the visions of the worlds past present and future. Almost unbearable she started crying but then her tears turned into crystals as her eyes glowed white, and she began to see the beauty and creation of all the universe. She reawakens. Master Shao Li giver her his old ancient fist weapons and she is now able to punch like a lightning bolt. "Thunder Hands", He chuckles. "That's what they use to call me once a long time ago." Asylus was very grateful and set out on her path to fight for those in need and to never fall into the greed or darkness that consumes so many hearts and souls.
